tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T18 at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament to earn conditional-exempt status for the PGA TOUR China Series' season. Will join his older brother, Wen Yi Huang, the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament medalist, as a Series' member this season.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Attempted to qualify for the PGA TOUR China Series but was unsuccessful. Open-qualified into one tournament, the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open, where he missed the cut.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was 66th in 2015 at the Chongqing Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T48th in Total Eagles on the PGA Tour China Series.
